# Debugging Race Conditions in Node.js Express with PostgreSQL Connection Pool

## Problem Description
Intermittent 500 errors occurring under load when multiple concurrent requests access a shared PostgreSQL connection pool, suggesting a race condition in connection management.

## Step 1: Reproduce the Issue

